{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Clean 3-tier menu ⭐\n      \n\n        \n        \n          ● Anthropic AI Ambassador\n          Your team should be using AI.Let me show you how.\n          Hands-on Claude training for teams that want to stop experimenting and start shipping. Customized to your industry, your workflows, your people.\n        \n\n        \n        \n\n          \n          \n            \n              \n                Lunch & Learn\n                60–90 min · In-person or virtual\n              \n              \n                Free\n                Limited time\n              \n            \n            I come to you. Your conference room, your team, your questions. Walk away with 3-5 AI workflows you can use Monday morning. No pitch, no slides — just building.\n          \n\n          \n          \n            \n              \n                1-on-1 Coaching\n                Flexible scheduling · Virtual or in-person\n              \n              \n                $250/hr\n              \n            \n            For the founder, VP, or team lead who wants to go deep before rolling AI out to the org. Learn to think in prompts, build agents, and evaluate what's real vs. hype.\n          \n\n          \n          \n            \n              \n                Team Workshop\n                Half-day or full-day · Up to 20 people\n              \n              \n                $5K–$15K\n                +$100/seat after 20\n              \n            \n            Your whole team, building real things in one room. I tailor the curriculum to your stack — whether that's devs shipping with Claude Code, PMs automating workflows, or ops teams cutting manual work in half.\n          \n\n        \n\n        \n          Larger programs and ongoing engagements available — let's talk","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1774746765083}
