{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Story-driven with embedded Tally ⭐\n      Lead with the mission, show what partners get, embed the Tally form right on the page (no redirect).\n\n      \n        \n        \n          ClaudeOC Impact Labs\n          Real problems.Real builders.Real solutions.\n          We pair Orange County nonprofits, hospitals, schools, and government agencies with AI builders who want their work to matter. You bring the problem — we bring the engineers.\n        \n\n        \n        \n          What partner organizations receive:\n          \n            \n              🛠️ A dedicated build team\n              Engineers matched to your problem\n            \n            \n              💰 Up to $5K in event support\n              We cover the logistics\n            \n            \n              🔑 API credits for all builders\n              $50/person, $500 for winners\n            \n            \n              🏆 Working prototype delivered\n              Not a pitch deck — a tool you can use\n            \n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          Who this is for:\n          \n            🏥 Healthcare\n            🎓 Education\n            🏛️ Local Government\n            ♻️ Sustainability\n            🤝 Nonprofits\n          \n        \n\n        \n        \n          Tally Form Embed\n          tally.so/r/Y5ZolB\n          Org name · Type · Description · Website\n          \"Know an org with a real problem? Tell us about it.\"\n        \n\n        \n        \n          \"Technology should amplify human resilience, not replace it.\"\n          — Travis Johnson, ClaudeOC","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1774746901896}
